## License Compliance

Cloud Gallery is designed to be license-compliant:

### ✅ Commercial Use
- All dependencies allow commercial use
- No GPL or restrictive licenses
- MIT and Apache 2.0 friendly licenses

### ✅ Modification
- All dependencies allow modification
- Source code availability maintained
- Attribution requirements followed

### ✅ Distribution
- All dependencies allow distribution
- License notices included
- No additional restrictions

### ✅ Patent Rights
- MIT and Apache 2.0 provide patent grants
- No patent retaliation clauses
- Freedom from patent litigation

